I have been on numberous PoF raids and had to break in to a full spawn on many occassions. I have seen this done in a few different ways. <br>
<br>
1) Duke it out at portal til its safe (usually doesnt work) <br>
<br>
2) Beeline for west camp and duke it out (usually doesnt work) <br>
<br>
3) Beeline for north camp and camp out as many as possible hoping a cleric makes it out, then drag and rez. (works usually) <br>
<br>
4) Person runs in solo and trains to Fetid Fiend house and runs in big circles with all the mobs. Group comes in and sets up at west camp or by Fetid Fiend House. Group then picks off parts of the train as it can manage til its dead. Trainer is usually best done by Bard. (most efective strategy I've seen). <br>
<br>
Does anyone know or do other strategies ? what has worked for you in the past ? <br>
